dct_description_sm: Stockholms Enskilda Bank. Selected buildings are illustrated. Inset: Gamla Stan = The Old Town. Index of Enskilda Bank branches on margin. Description of points of interest, useful information, index of museums, restaurants, hotels, etc. on margin and continuing on verso. Verso: inset of Stockholm and its surroundings (1:65,000). 1965
